1
00:00:02,495 --> 00:00:03,777
大帝在来的路上
The Emperor is coming.

2
00:00:04,270 --> 00:00:05,811
那我们得跟他的继位者
We must avoid dishonor

3
00:00:05,850 --> 00:00:08,517
搞好关系免遭羞辱
by cultivating goodwill with his successor.

4
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:09,573
你是指卡里古拉?
You mean Caligula?

5
00:00:09,575 --> 00:00:11,075
你要是知道我们为何来此
You may not be so keen to welcome us

6
00:00:11,077 --> 00:00:12,676
可能就不会这么热烈欢迎我们了
when you find out why we're here.

7
00:00:12,678 --> 00:00:15,980
告诉我彼得在哪 我们就停手
Tell me where Peter is, and we'll stop.

8
00:00:15,982 --> 00:00:18,916
我不觉得到撒玛利亚会有何益处 腓力
I don't think it will be any better in Samaria for them.

9
00:00:18,918 --> 00:00:20,684
我帮你
Let me help you.

10
00:00:22,221 --> 00:00:26,090
来这途中 我看见四只秃鹰
On the journey here, I saw four vultures.

11
00:00:26,092 --> 00:00:28,726
这地方让你见到幻象
This place gives you visions.

12
00:00:28,728 --> 00:00:30,827
西门魔法师!
Simon the sorcerer!

13
00:00:32,598 --> 00:00:35,766
他觉得自己比我厉害
He thinks he can do what I can't.

14
00:00:35,768 --> 00:00:39,370
奉耶稣之名 我将你从监牢中释放
In the name of Jesus, I release you from your prison.

15
00:00:41,874 --> 00:00:43,207
你是否悔改你的罪?
Do you repent your sins?

16
00:00:43,209 --> 00:00:44,209
我悔改
I do.

17
00:00:44,210 --> 00:00:45,609
把彼得的消息告诉扫罗
Tell Saul about Peter.

18
00:00:45,611 --> 00:00:47,378
- 他往北去了  - 哪里?
- He headed north.  - Where?

19
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:49,113
大马士革
Damascus.

