25
00:01:00,626 --> 00:01:02,459
我们都能高枕无忧了
once Saul leaves for Damascus.

26
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:04,400
{\an8}协调: 影子

27
00:01:02,461 --> 00:01:04,528
果真如此?
Really?

28
00:01:04,530 --> 00:01:06,964
你要确保他不会
Your task is to make sure he doesn't bring

29
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:06,600
{\an8}翻译: 飘飘行天下 小黄不小黄 猫呗

30
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:08,800
{\an8}翻译: 舒舒 鸟生鱼汤 波特妹子

31
00:01:06,966 --> 00:01:09,967
再让耶路撒冷陷入暴乱...
his campaign of violence back to Jerusalem...

32
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,000
{\an8}校对: 飘飘行天下 影子

33
00:01:09,969 --> 00:01:12,703
尤其不能在提庇留回罗马之前
not before Tiberius has left for Rome.

34
00:01:12,705 --> 00:01:14,872
那我要如何确保?
And how exactly do I do that?

35
00:01:14,874 --> 00:01:16,507
你同他一起去
You're going with him.

36
00:01:22,548 --> 00:01:25,683
我可不认为年轻活泼就该是这副模样
I won't defend this as youthful high spirits.

37
00:01:25,685 --> 00:01:28,952
恕我冒昧... 我也很不想这样说...
Forgive me... and it pains me to say this...

38
00:01:28,954 --> 00:01:31,722
这可不是未来君主应有的行为
This is not the behavior of a future emperor.

39
00:01:31,724 --> 00:01:33,590
没错
I agree.

40
00:01:33,592 --> 00:01:35,859
要能承担起将来的责任
Caligula has a great deal to learn

41
00:01:35,861 --> 00:01:38,829
卡里古拉要学的东西还很多
about the responsibilities he will carry.

42
00:01:38,831 --> 00:01:41,331
但他同这个犹太人阿格里帕整日厮混
But it doesn't help that he spends so much time

43
00:01:41,333 --> 00:01:43,300
可毫无益处
with this Jew, Agrippa.

44
00:01:43,302 --> 00:01:45,502
近墨者黑
He's a malign influence.

45
00:01:45,504 --> 00:01:48,739
叫醒他们 让他们出去
Wake them. Get them out of here.

46
00:01:48,741 --> 00:01:50,507
可不能让克劳迪娅看见
Claudia mustn't see this.

47
00:01:50,509 --> 00:01:53,043
不能让克劳迪娅看见什么?
Claudia mustn't see what?

48
00:02:02,755 --> 00:02:08,692
他们怎敢把我的名字写在烂醉的妓女身上
How dare they scrawl my name on a wine-soaked whore.

49
00:02:08,694 --> 00:02:12,063
要是这淫行在屋里留下一丝痕迹
I will not set foot inside this room again

50
00:02:12,065 --> 00:02:15,332
我便再不踏足半步
until every sign of this debauchery is gone.

51
00:02:25,010 --> 00:02:27,411
要是能在日落前赶到拉马塔教区
If we reach Ramatha before sunset,

52
00:02:27,413 --> 00:02:29,680
应该就能在两日内到达大马士革
we should make Damascus in two days.

53
00:02:29,682 --> 00:02:31,248
扫罗 那里远在70英里外
Saul, that's over 70 Miles away,

54
00:02:31,250 --> 00:02:32,816
你难道想一日内赶到?
and you want to do that in a day,

55
00:02:32,818 --> 00:02:34,985
这一路都是荒漠和山路
over open deserts and Mountain tracks

56
00:02:34,987 --> 00:02:36,220
还是三伏天呢
in the hottest month?

57
00:02:36,222 --> 00:02:38,055
看起来我们新来的人
It would appear our new recruit

58
00:02:38,057 --> 00:02:39,990
更想窝在家里呢
would be happier staying at home.

59
00:02:41,393 --> 00:02:44,728
我可不要走这么快 会要了命的
I'm not going to kill myself marching at that pace.

60
00:02:50,436 --> 00:02:52,870
听说腓力需要我们
We get word that Philip needs us.

61
00:02:52,872 --> 00:02:55,706
必须有人去撒玛利亚
Somebody has to go to Samaria.

62
00:02:55,708 --> 00:02:57,374
那我们怎么办?
So what do we do?

63
00:02:57,376 --> 00:02:59,743
就躲在一个地窖里
We hide in a cellar.

64
00:03:11,924 --> 00:03:13,257
西门 我明白你的心情
Simon, I feel the same way.

65
00:03:13,259 --> 00:03:15,392
但只要扫罗一日在那...
But as long as Saul's out there...

66
00:03:15,394 --> 00:03:17,728
我知道跟腓力会合很危险
I know going to join Philip is dangerous,

67
00:03:17,730 --> 00:03:19,596
但我不想当个懦夫
but I feel like a coward.

68
00:03:19,598 --> 00:03:21,965
那么现在你不必当懦夫了
Well, now you don't need to.

69
00:03:21,967 --> 00:03:23,734
扫罗走了
Saul's gone.

70
00:03:23,736 --> 00:03:26,804
他离开了耶路撒冷
He's left Jerusalem.

71
00:03:26,806 --> 00:03:30,207
约翰 我们今夜就赶去撒玛利亚
We'll go to Samaria tonight, John.

72
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:44,288
玛利亚? 是我... 约亚拿
Mary? It's me... Joanna.

73
00:03:44,290 --> 00:03:46,089
你在这里做什么?
What are you doing here?

74
00:03:46,091 --> 00:03:47,825
我是随安提帕的家宰来的
I'm here with the house of Antipas,

75
00:03:47,827 --> 00:03:49,193
来服侍希罗底
maid-servant to Herodias.

76
00:03:49,195 --> 00:03:51,528
你是在宫殿里作工吗?
Are you working in the palace?

77
00:03:56,902 --> 00:03:59,770
我们得小心 这里的人与我们信仰不同
We must be cautious. None here share our faith.

78
00:04:01,841 --> 00:04:03,006
彼得也在这里吗?
Is Peter here, too?

79
00:04:03,008 --> 00:04:06,443
他在城里... 安全躲着呢
He's in the city... hiding, safe.

80
00:04:07,913 --> 00:04:11,715
自从耶稣治好我俩的病 我就整日想着你
I thought about you every day since Jesus cured us.

81
00:04:11,717 --> 00:04:14,518
我也想遵行他讲的道 但是...
I have tried to follow his word, but...

82
00:04:15,888 --> 00:04:18,322
我听说他已经死了
I heard he was dead.

83
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:24,795
约亚拿...
Joanna...

84
00:04:24,797 --> 00:04:26,396
耶稣并没死
Jesus isn't dead.

85
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:29,967
在他上十字架前
Before they crucified him,

86
00:04:29,969 --> 00:04:33,103
他就告诉我们他将在三日后复活
he told us he would rise after three days,

87
00:04:33,105 --> 00:04:36,073
后来果真如此
and he did.

88
00:04:36,075 --> 00:04:37,875
他活得好好的
He's very much alive.

89
00:04:37,877 --> 00:04:39,443
是真的
No. It's true.

90
00:04:39,445 --> 00:04:41,144
他先来找我
He came to me first.

91
00:04:41,146 --> 00:04:43,313
我与他同坐 与他同吃
I've sat with him, eaten with him.

92
00:04:43,315 --> 00:04:46,450
他真如他所说
He is who he said he was.

93
00:04:48,087 --> 00:04:49,686
是弥赛亚
He is the Messiah.

94
00:05:10,509 --> 00:05:13,510
我一度还挺喜欢阿格里帕 但是如今...
I was fond of Agrippa once, but now...

95
00:05:16,782 --> 00:05:19,049
我该处死他吗?
Should I have him killed?

96
00:05:23,622 --> 00:05:25,956
不用
No.

97
00:05:25,958 --> 00:05:28,158
您带卡里古拉回罗马
Take Caligula back to Rome with you,

98
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:31,061
由我丈夫来处置阿格里帕
and my husband will deal with Agrippa.

99
00:05:31,997 --> 00:05:33,397
彼拉多是个好巡抚
Pilate is a good governor.

100
00:05:33,399 --> 00:05:34,865
您只要看看
You only have to see

101
00:05:34,867 --> 00:05:37,401
耶路撒冷清静无事的街道就知道他...
the trouble-free streets of Jerusalem to see what...

102
00:05:37,403 --> 00:05:40,737
为了让你丈夫升官你真是煞费苦心
You work hard to promote your husband.

103
00:05:42,374 --> 00:05:45,742
等我把他升迁到罗马去的时候
I'm sure he will benefit from your wisdom

104
00:05:45,744 --> 00:05:49,112
你的智慧一定对他大有裨益
when I promote him to a position in Rome.

105
00:05:55,654 --> 00:05:57,721
谢谢您
Thank you.

106
00:05:59,491 --> 00:06:02,726
我不知道我更高兴的是哪件事...
I don't know what pleases me more...

107
00:06:02,728 --> 00:06:06,163
是可以去罗马多陪陪您
the thought of spending more time in your company in Rome

108
00:06:06,165 --> 00:06:08,632
还是终于可以...
or finally being able to...

109
00:06:17,042 --> 00:06:18,542
有什么问题吗?
Is there something wrong?

110
00:06:18,544 --> 00:06:20,143
没有
No.

111
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:25,248
感觉有点凉 没什么
Just a chill. That's all.

112
00:06:25,250 --> 00:06:27,584
不要低估了彼得
Do not underestimate Peter.

113
00:06:27,586 --> 00:06:31,121
他是个卖狗皮膏药的 但是非常在行
He is a snake-oil trader, but a good one.

114
00:06:31,123 --> 00:06:36,126
他先告诉大家他们有麻烦了...
First, he tells the people that they have a problem...

115
00:06:36,128 --> 00:06:40,263
说他们杀了神派给他们的人
that they killed the man sent to them by God.

116
00:06:40,265 --> 00:06:44,134
然后他再说他有解决方法
Then he tells them that he has the answer.

117
00:06:44,136 --> 00:06:45,969
他们只需要
All they have to do

118
00:06:45,971 --> 00:06:48,805
忏悔 然后跳到河里去就可以了
is repent and throw themselves in the river.

119
00:06:51,410 --> 00:06:52,776
他就不能消停会吗?
Does he ever stop?

120
00:06:52,778 --> 00:06:55,479
我从来没见过为了毁灭敌人
I never saw a man with so much energy

121
00:06:55,481 --> 00:06:58,081
如此干劲十足的人
for the destruction of his enemies.

122
00:06:58,083 --> 00:07:03,520
我们现在... 坐在这里... 作为被选中的少数人
And here we sit... now... the chosen few,

123
00:07:03,522 --> 00:07:07,357
我们的使命是根除这个异教
whose work it is to stamp out this heresy

124
00:07:07,359 --> 00:07:10,527
不能让它从耶路撒冷
before it spreads from Jerusalem

125
00:07:10,529 --> 00:07:15,132
散布到叙利亚 吕大 以马忤斯 甚至是马察达去
and takes control of Syria, Lydda, Emmaus, and even Masada,

126
00:07:15,134 --> 00:07:19,569
不能让彼得这个渔夫把他那虚假的解药
before Peter the fisherman can sell the whole world

127
00:07:19,571 --> 00:07:22,039
卖给全世界
his fake cure.

128
00:07:35,372 --> 00:07:40,810
这里大多数人都认为罗马人很堕落
Most people here believe all Romans to be degenerate.

129
00:07:44,582 --> 00:07:47,083
你想证明他们是对的吗?
Are you determined to prove them right?

130
00:07:47,085 --> 00:07:48,951
你听到什么了吗?
Do you hear something?

131
00:07:48,953 --> 00:07:51,521
噪音...
A noise...

132
00:07:51,523 --> 00:07:53,690
就像母牛在叫
like a cow breaking wind.

133
00:07:55,026 --> 00:07:57,327
最糟的是 你侮辱了我的妻子
On top of that, you insult my wife.

134
00:07:57,329 --> 00:08:01,631
如果一个人的妻子是婊子的女儿
Is it possible to insult a man's wife

135
00:08:01,633 --> 00:08:03,766
还怎么侮辱她呢?
when she's the daughter of a whore?

136
00:08:07,505 --> 00:08:13,376
收回那些话 不然我就割了你的喉咙
Take back those words before I open your throat.

137
00:08:13,378 --> 00:08:14,977
来啊
Do it.

138
00:08:14,979 --> 00:08:17,579
我想着提庇留会怎么对付你
I'd almost die happy

139
00:08:17,581 --> 00:08:19,882
会死得很开心的
thinking about what Tiberius would do to you.

140
00:09:04,963 --> 00:09:07,597
起来啊 你这头蠢马!
Get up, you stupid animal!

141
00:09:21,780 --> 00:09:22,845
走啊
Come on.

142
00:09:24,315 --> 00:09:26,916
我本该下手的
I should've done it.

143
00:09:26,918 --> 00:09:29,419
他说了这种话我就该割了他的喉咙
I should've slit his throat after what he said.

144
00:09:29,421 --> 00:09:31,821
要是你杀了他 你还能活多久?
And how long would you have lived if you had?

145
00:09:31,823 --> 00:09:34,657
然后把阿格里帕也杀了
And done the same with Agrippa.

146
00:09:34,659 --> 00:09:36,492
你也可以忽视他们
Or your could ignore them both

147
00:09:36,494 --> 00:09:39,562
期待一下罗马的生活
and look forward to life in Rome.

148
00:09:39,564 --> 00:09:43,800
我还从来没见过如此居心叵测 卑鄙狠毒
I've never come across such treacherous, poisonous,

149
00:09:43,802 --> 00:09:46,002
渴望权力的阴谋家
power-hungry schemers.

150
00:09:47,472 --> 00:09:49,338
怎么了?
What is it?

151
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:51,240
我希望那里的一切
I'm looking forward to everything there

152
00:09:51,242 --> 00:09:53,276
都能少点...
being a lot less...

153
00:09:53,278 --> 00:09:54,310
犹太风格
Jewish.

154
00:09:54,312 --> 00:09:55,445
你呢?
Aren't you?

155
00:09:55,447 --> 00:09:58,481
你在说什么 克劳迪娅?
What are you talking about, Claudia?

156
00:09:58,483 --> 00:10:03,152
提庇留要升你去罗马了
Tiberius has offered you a position in Rome.

157
00:10:06,958 --> 00:10:08,291
终于
At last.

158
00:10:09,727 --> 00:10:13,963
我们终于可以离开这地方了
We can finally leave this place.

159
00:10:13,965 --> 00:10:16,232
我们只需要
All we have to do

160
00:10:16,234 --> 00:10:17,733
做好我们的事
is play our part

161
00:10:17,735 --> 00:10:21,137
让阿格里帕和卡里古拉分开
in keeping Agrippa and Caligula away from each other.

162
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:25,575
我奉圣父 圣子
I baptize you in the name of the father

163
00:10:25,577 --> 00:10:28,344
和圣灵的名为你施洗
and of the son and of the Holy Spirit.

164
00:10:33,084 --> 00:10:35,885
彼得! 约翰!
Peter! John!

165
00:10:41,092 --> 00:10:44,126
见到你们真高兴
It's so good to see you both.

166
00:10:44,128 --> 00:10:48,030
朋友们 如今我们将自己交托给耶稣
My friends, today, we commit ourselves to Jesus,

167
00:10:48,032 --> 00:10:51,133
而这两个人认识他
who these two men knew

168
00:10:51,135 --> 00:10:54,437
并从他那里得到了圣灵的能力
and from him received the power of the Holy Spirit.

169
00:10:56,574 --> 00:10:58,641
如果连弥赛亚的名字也不敢说
How can we celebrate the Messiah

170
00:10:58,643 --> 00:11:01,143
还如何颂扬他?
when we dare not say his name?

171
00:11:01,145 --> 00:11:02,278
我害怕
I'm scared.

172
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:04,447
不必害怕
Don't be.

173
00:11:04,449 --> 00:11:07,149
我们共同祈祷 你的信仰便可给你力量
Your faith will bring you strength when we pray together.

174
00:11:09,354 --> 00:11:11,220
苦撒
Chuza.

175
00:11:11,222 --> 00:11:13,189
我没想到你会现在回来
I wasn't expecting you back.

176
00:11:13,191 --> 00:11:15,758
这是我的丈夫
This is my husband.

177
00:11:15,760 --> 00:11:17,159
那这位是谁?
And who is this?

178
00:11:17,161 --> 00:11:18,661
玛利亚
Mary.

179
00:11:18,663 --> 00:11:21,430
我才刚刚开始在这个宫殿工作
I only just started work here in the palace,

180
00:11:21,432 --> 00:11:22,665
但我认识约亚拿...
but I know Joanna from...

181
00:11:22,667 --> 00:11:24,567
集市上认识的
From the market.

182
00:11:24,569 --> 00:11:26,569
我们以前常在集市上碰到
We used to see each other at the market.

