My wife has come under some bad influences recently.

186
00:11:37,315 --> 00:11:39,749
我不想再发生这种事
I don't want it to happen again.

187
00:11:39,751 --> 00:11:42,518
不要担心 我会保护她的
Don't worry. I'll keep her from harm.

188
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:50,426
你的丈夫不知道你的信仰吗?
Your husband doesn't know about your faith?

189
00:11:50,428 --> 00:11:51,827
他知道的
He does.

190
00:11:51,829 --> 00:11:55,264
安全起见 我同意保密
I agreed to hide it to protect us both.

191
00:11:55,266 --> 00:11:56,699
安提帕和希罗底
It was Antipas and Herodias

192
00:11:56,701 --> 00:11:58,467
把施洗者约翰的头砍了
that had John the baptist beheaded.

