Leave us.

209
00:12:51,155 --> 00:12:54,789
我还要为你姐姐希罗底做事
I... I have work to do for your sister, Herodias.

210
00:12:56,661 --> 00:13:00,096
她不会介意你和我共度片刻
She won't mind if you spend a few minutes with me.

211
00:13:03,167 --> 00:13:04,533
我亲爱的弟弟
My dear brother.

212
00:13:08,673 --> 00:13:10,940
我早同你讲过...
I've told you before...

213
00:13:10,942 --> 00:13:14,543
别让我逮到你玩弄我的东西
don't let me catch you playing with my things.

214
00:13:31,663 --> 00:13:32,728
扫罗
Saul.

215
00:13:34,298 --> 00:13:35,364
扫罗!
Saul!

216
00:13:37,468 --> 00:13:40,703
扫罗 这地方太疯狂了
Saul, this place is madness.

217
00:13:40,705 --> 00:13:42,571
要是你没找到他呢?
What if you don't find him?

218
00:13:42,573 --> 00:13:44,707
要是彼得根本不在大马士革呢?
What if Peter's not even in Damascus?

219
00:13:44,709 --> 00:13:46,575
我们要追到安提阿吗?
Do we march onto Antioch?

220
00:13:46,577 --> 00:13:50,513
你究竟来这里干嘛? 嗯?
Why are you even here? Huh?

221
00:13:50,515 --> 00:13:52,715
我来这里是因为受命来此
I'm here because I was ordered to be here

222
00:13:52,717 --> 00:13:54,850
我们听命于同一人
by the same man we both answer to.

223
00:13:54,852 --> 00:13:57,219
那你就该协助完成这一使命
Then you should be helping this mission,

224
00:13:57,221 --> 00:13:59,355
而非拖拉时间
not slowing it down.

225
00:14:00,692 --> 00:14:02,591
你为什么这么恨彼得?
Why do you hate Peter so much?

226
00:14:02,593 --> 00:14:05,094
因为他的话太荒谬
Because his claims are ridiculous.

227
00:14:05,096 --> 00:14:07,697
因为说他是神拣选的
Because the idea that God would use him

228
00:14:07,699 --> 00:14:08,998
神的旨意的器皿
as an instrument of his will

229
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,933
让他传扬新的弥赛亚的道
to spread the word of a new Messiah

230
00:14:10,935 --> 00:14:13,736
这想法... 太荒谬了
is... is ridiculous.

231
00:14:13,738 --> 00:14:17,440
人们怎能相信造物主会选择
How can people believe that the creator would choose

232
00:14:17,442 --> 00:14:20,509
一个卑微的渔夫来表达他的旨意?
a simple fisherman to articulate his message?

233
00:14:20,511 --> 00:14:23,112
不 不
No. No.

234
00:14:23,114 --> 00:14:24,847
他会选择一个
He would choose a man

235
00:14:24,849 --> 00:14:27,550
比渔村之徒眼界开阔的人
who knew a world outside of a fishing village,

236
00:14:27,552 --> 00:14:30,453
而不是替骗子耶稣散播谎言的人
not a man who spreads lies about an impostor Jesus,

237
00:14:30,455 --> 00:14:34,890
会选一个为他的旨意
but a man who can add beauty and power and truth

238
00:14:34,892 --> 00:14:36,892
增光添彩的人... 比如...
to his message... a man like...

239
00:14:44,702 --> 00:14:46,168
好吧
Yeah.

240
00:15:03,254 --> 00:15:04,887
扫罗
Saul.

241
00:15:08,793 --> 00:15:10,893
扫罗
Saul.

242
