你为什么逼迫我?
Why do you persecute me?

243
00:15:16,968 --> 00:15:18,367
你是谁?
Who are you?

244
00:15:18,369 --> 00:15:21,437
我就是
I am Jesus.

245
00:15:21,439 --> 00:15:23,038
你所逼迫的耶稣
Whom you persecute.

246
00:15:25,009 --> 00:15:26,575
不
No.

