The man who brought us is a remarkable man.

267
00:17:25,170 --> 00:17:28,171
不管在沙漠中发生什么事 我们都不能放弃
Whatever happened to him in the desert, we can't give up.

268
00:17:28,173 --> 00:17:30,440
我们必须找到彼得和追随他的人
We must find Peter and his followers.

