00:19:00,032 --> 00:19:02,165
扫罗在大马士革
Saul is in Damascus.

291
00:19:03,268 --> 00:19:05,101
你来到这里给我们灌输
You arrive here and you fill our heads

292
00:19:05,103 --> 00:19:07,103
救主耶稣基督的力量
with the power of Jesus Christ the savior,
