293
00:19:07,105 --> 00:19:09,239
却一见危险就要退缩
and now you cower at the first sign of danger.

294
00:19:09,241 --> 00:19:10,241
亚拿尼亚!
Ananias!

295
00:19:10,242 --> 00:19:12,409
大数人扫罗 他想杀了我...
Saul of Tarsus, who wants me dead...

296
00:19:12,411 --> 00:19:14,444
想杀了我们所有人... 他在这里
who wants us all dead... is here.

297
00:19:14,446 --> 00:19:16,213
那我该怎么做?
And what am I supposed to do?

298
00:19:16,215 --> 00:19:18,148
告诉我妻子 先不要生孩子了
Tell my wife, don't have our child yet.

299
00:19:18,150 --> 00:19:19,983
赶紧离开这里?
We have to leave the city?

300
00:19:19,985 --> 00:19:21,251
留下吧
Stay.

301
00:19:22,921 --> 00:19:25,055
留下来
Stay.

302
00:19:25,057 --> 00:19:27,090
我们共同寻求力量
And we'll find strength together.

303
00:19:28,560 --> 00:19:30,594
倚靠耶稣
Trust in Jesus.

304
00:19:33,098 --> 00:19:36,833
让圣灵进入你困苦的肢体
Let the Holy Spirit into your troubled limbs.

305
00:19:36,835 --> 00:19:39,769
他赐给你永生
He brings you eternal life.

306
00:19:49,748 --> 00:19:52,782
你当信服耶稣基督
Have faith in Jesus Christ.

307
00:19:52,784 --> 00:19:56,620
他便是那路 是真理 是生命
He is the way, the truth, and the life.

308
00:19:58,290 --> 00:20:01,591
我们祈祷新的信徒
We pray that all our new believers

309
00:20:01,593 --> 00:20:04,327
都蒙受圣灵
receive the Holy Spirit.

310
00:20:04,329 --> 00:20:05,996
难以置信
Unbelievable.

311
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:14,271
我们向神悔改 信靠我主 蒙他悦纳
We enter God's kingdom by repentance and faith
302 

312
00:20:14,273 --> 00:20:17,173
进入神的国
