And my seal on it says you will get the job.

318
00:20:49,174 --> 00:20:52,542
凯撒 我不知该如何表达谢意
Caesar, I don't know how to show you my gratitude.

319
00:20:52,544 --> 00:20:54,144
那就勤勉工作吧
By doing the job well.

320
00:20:55,314 --> 00:20:59,249
