And by always listening to your wife's advice.

321
00:21:03,855 --> 00:21:06,790
这下好了 这是正式命令
There. It's official.

322
00:21:06,792 --> 00:21:08,858
永远听从你的妻子
Always listen to your wife.

323
00:21:12,297 --> 00:21:13,997
我会记住的!
I won't forget this!

324
00:21:13,999 --> 00:21:15,565
