00:26:25,759 --> 00:26:28,760
不管梦到什么 不过是梦而已
Whatever it was, it was just a dream.

373
00:26:30,764 --> 00:26:31,997
怎么了?
What is it?

374
00:26:31,999 --> 00:26:34,766
什么东西这么可怕?
What was so terrible?

375
00:26:34,768 --> 00:26:37,002
没什么
It's nothing.

376
00:26:45,513 --> 00:26:48,313
亚拿尼亚
Ananias.

377
00:27:14,842 --> 00:27:16,308
亚拿尼亚
Ananias.

378
00:27:17,945 --> 00:27:20,078
主
Lord.

379
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:22,147
往直街去
Go to the street called straight.

380
00:27:22,149 --> 00:27:26,084
找一个大数人
Ask for a man from Tarsus.

381
00:27:26,086 --> 00:27:28,020
名叫扫罗
His name is Saul.

382
00:27:30,391 --> 00:27:33,458
但我知道这人怎样在耶路撒冷多多苦害
But I know the harm that this man has done

383
00:27:33,460 --> 00:27:34,859
你的圣徒
to your people in Jerusalem.

384
00:27:34,961 --> 00:27:37,496
他是我所拣选的器皿
He is my chosen instrument.

385
00:27:37,498 --> 00:27:41,066
要在外邦人和君王并以色列人面前
He will proclaim my name to the gentiles and their kings

386
00:27:41,068 --> 00:27:44,036
宣扬我的名
and the people of Israel.

387
00:27:51,779 --> 00:27:52,844
什么?
What?

388
00:27:52,846 --> 00:27:56,214
住手 伙计! 你不能!
Stop, mate! You mustn't!

389
00:27:57,518 --> 00:27:58,784
亚拿尼亚
Ananias.

390
00:28:06,382 --> 00:28:07,971
得有人回耶路撒冷
Someone needs to go to Jerusalem

391
00:28:07,973 --> 00:28:09,172
把这发生的事告诉该亚法
and tell Caiaphas what's happening.

392
00:28:09,174 --> 00:28:10,340
该告诉他什么呢?
And tell him what, exactly?

393
00:28:10,342 --> 00:28:12,842
让他知道他的红人 阻止亵渎神灵之人
That his golden boy, his great weapon

394
00:28:12,844 --> 00:28:14,647
东山再起的得力干将
against the rise of these blasphemers

395
00:28:14,662 --> 00:28:15,795
正在黑暗中
is sitting in the dark

396
00:28:15,797 --> 00:28:18,397
把自己饿死?
starving himself to death?

397
00:28:18,399 --> 00:28:20,132
或许我能帮忙
Perhaps I can help.

398
00:28:22,670 --> 00:28:26,138
我有消息要给大数人扫罗...
I have a message for Saul of Tarsus...

399
00:28:26,140 --> 00:28:27,740
很重要的消息
an important one.

400
00:28:27,742 --> 00:28:29,175
来自何人?
From whom?

401
00:28:29,177 --> 00:28:32,578
来自... 某个对他很了解的人...
From... someone who knows him well...

402
00:28:32,580 --> 00:28:34,680
可以说 比任何人都了解他
knows him better than anyone, I'd say.

403
00:28:36,184 --> 00:28:37,316
那么你是...?
And you are...?

404
00:28:37,318 --> 00:28:39,352
我是亚拿尼亚
I am Ananias.

405
00:28:47,628 --> 00:28:50,529
他来了吗?
I.. is he here? 

406
00:28:50,531 --> 00:28:52,732
亚拿尼亚在哪儿? 在这里吗?
Where's Ananias? Is he here?

407
00:28:52,734 --> 00:28:54,734
- 我在这  - 哦 哦
- I'm here.  - Oh. Oh.

408
00:28:54,736 --> 00:28:57,436
求你... 救救我
Save me from this... please.

409
00:29:06,147 --> 00:29:08,614
他拣选了你 叫你明白他的旨意
He has chosen you to know his will

410
00:29:08,616 --> 00:29:11,450
又得见那义者
and to see the righteous one

411
00:29:11,452 --> 00:29:15,454
听他口中所出的声音
and to hear the words from his mouth.

412
00:29:38,446 --> 00:29:41,781
他能看见了
He can see.

413
00:29:41,783 --> 00:29:42,915
扫罗又能看见了
Saul can see again.

414
00:29:45,520 --> 00:29:46,952
我能看见了!
I can see!

415
00:29:46,954 --> 00:29:50,823
谢谢你 谢谢你 谢谢你 
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you.

416
00:29:55,430 --> 00:29:58,964
把我和卡里古拉分开又把我困在此处
Separate me from Caligula and keep me in this place,

417
00:29:58,966 --> 00:30:01,000
至少也该尊重我
but at least show me some respect.

418
00:30:01,002 --> 00:30:03,803
照我所说惩罚这些亵渎神灵的人
Do as I ask and punish these blasphemers.

419
00:30:03,805 --> 00:30:06,572
这是你的职责 你要做出表率
It's your duty. Make an example of them.

420
00:30:06,574 --> 00:30:09,508
职责? 什么时候你开始知道职责了?
Duty? Since when have you had any thoughts of duty?

421
00:30:09,510 --> 00:30:13,479
他是对的... 尽管我质疑他的动机
He's right... though I do question his reasons.

422
00:30:13,481 --> 00:30:16,749
他对这个女人有兴趣
He has an interest in this woman.

423
00:30:28,229 --> 00:30:30,729
苦撒 我的家宰
Chuza, as my chief Steward,

424
00:30:30,731 --> 00:30:32,798
你知道背叛的后果
you know the consequences of betrayal.

425
00:30:32,800 --> 00:30:34,400
果真如此吗?
Is it true?

426
00:30:35,536 --> 00:30:38,737
你的妻子是那个人称耶稣的拿撒勒人的信徒吗?
Is your wife a follower of the Nazarene they call Jesus?

427
00:30:38,739 --> 00:30:41,740
我听见你向他祷告
I heard you pray to him.

428
00:30:41,742 --> 00:30:43,876
只要...
Just...

429
00:30:43,878 --> 00:30:46,178
实话实说就好
give us the truth.

430
00:30:49,317 --> 00:30:51,750
事实是... 那个 呃...
The truth is... that, uh...

431
00:30:51,752 --> 00:30:54,053
事实是...
The truth is...

432
00:30:54,055 --> 00:30:58,057
我的妻子约亚拿自从结婚以来
that my wife, Joanna, ever since we were married,

433
00:30:58,059 --> 00:30:59,592
都会不时发疯
has had fits of madness.

434
00:30:59,594 --> 00:31:02,228
自从有了关于那个拿撒勒人
Since all the talk began of the Nazarene

435
00:31:02,230 --> 00:31:04,230
死而复生的传言 她就...
coming back to life after being crucified, she's...

436
00:31:05,466 --> 00:31:07,399
嗯 她就整日想着此事
well, she's been taken by the idea.

437
00:31:07,401 --> 00:31:11,437
有时她会臆想自己在跟他说话
And sometimes she imagines she's talking to him.

438
00:31:11,439 --> 00:31:16,175
我怕有一天 她会陷入疯狂...
My fear is that one day, she'll slip into lunacy...

439
00:31:16,177 --> 00:31:18,444
无法恢复
and not return.

440
00:31:19,547 --> 00:31:24,517
你是说你的妻子并不是耶稣的信徒...
Your argument is that your wife isn't a follower of Jesus...

441
00:31:24,519 --> 00:31:26,051
她只是疯了?
she's just mad?

442
00:31:29,056 --> 00:31:30,890
女人 你又怎么说?
And what do you say, woman?

443
00:31:33,127 --> 00:31:34,393
你是... 疯了?
What are you... mad?

444
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:48,407
没错
It's true.

445
00:31:50,778 --> 00:31:53,779
我已不再鬼迷心窍
I was once cured of demons.

446
00:31:56,284 --> 00:31:58,918
我不允许我家有人向那个人祷告...
I do not allow prayers to that man in my household...

447
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:00,786
哪怕是臆想也不行
even imagined ones.

448
00:32:03,758 --> 00:32:05,124
管好你的妻子
Control your wife.

449
00:32:06,961 --> 00:32:09,028
够了 让他们走吧
Enough. Let them go.

450
00:32:10,031 --> 00:32:11,096
什么?!
What?!

451
00:32:11,098 --> 00:32:13,132
就这样?!
That's all?!

452
00:32:22,343 --> 00:32:24,109
你能恢复真是太好了
It's good to have you back.

453
00:32:25,713 --> 00:32:26,979
好吧 我敞开心扉
Well, I open my heart,

454
00:32:26,981 --> 00:32:29,949
感谢神宽恕了我
and I give my thanks to God for his forgiveness.

455
00:32:29,951 --> 00:32:33,485
在沙漠的时候... 发生了什么?
What happened to you... in the desert?

456
00:32:34,989 --> 00:32:36,455
我看见他
I saw him.

457
00:32:37,792 --> 00:32:40,559
亲眼所见
I saw.

458
00:32:43,664 --> 00:32:46,632
我看见耶稣基督 神的儿子
I saw Jesus Christ, the son of God.

459
00:32:47,768 --> 00:32:49,468
他就在这
And he's here.

460
00:32:50,805 --> 00:32:52,871
那些被我迫害的信徒
His presence is here on earth,

461
00:32:52,873 --> 00:32:56,342
就是他存在的见证
through those followers I persecuted.

462
00:32:56,344 --> 00:32:58,811
我曾经那么确定我是对的
I felt so sure that I was right,

463
00:32:58,813 --> 00:33:00,012
但我...
but I...

464
00:33:00,014 --> 00:33:02,181
我才是错了的人
I was the one that was wrong.

465
00:33:03,251 --> 00:33:05,784
我们所有人都...
All of us just...

466
00:33:05,786 --> 00:33:08,087
错了
wrong.

467
00:33:08,089 --> 00:33:10,489
我必须将功赎罪 必须这样
I have to make amends. I have to.

468
00:33:10,491 --> 00:33:13,626
所以我去了河边
So I'm going to the river

469
00:33:13,628 --> 00:33:16,795
接受了这个人的洗礼... 亚拿尼亚
to be baptized by this man... Ananias.

470
00:33:16,797 --> 00:33:20,299
而我恳求你们... 跟我一起
And I implore you... come with me.

471
00:33:20,301 --> 00:33:22,434
感受神的爱
Feel God's love.

472
00:33:22,436 --> 00:33:26,205
奉耶稣的名受洗
Be baptized in the name of Jesus.

473
00:34:24,832 --> 00:34:27,166
太荒唐了
This is ridiculous.

474
00:34:27,168 --> 00:34:30,102
你愚蠢的梦让我无法入睡
You're keeping me awake with your foolish dream.

475
00:34:30,104 --> 00:34:32,204
告诉我
Tell me now.

476
00:34:32,206 --> 00:34:34,306
你看到了什么?
What is it you're seeing?

477
00:34:36,344 --> 00:34:40,346
我看见... 提庇留 
I see... Tiberius.

478
00:34:40,348 --> 00:34:43,482
看见他被杀死在床上
I see him murdered in his bed.

479
00:34:46,087 --> 00:34:48,453
我还看到当他们用枕头捂住他的脸时
And I see him struggle

480
00:34:48,455 --> 00:34:51,090
他... 他不断挣扎
as... as they hold a pillow over his face.

481
00:34:51,092 --> 00:34:54,326
拿枕头的人是卡里古拉
The pillow is held by Caligula.

482
00:34:55,629 --> 00:34:57,363
胡说
Nonsense.

483
00:34:58,532 --> 00:35:02,267
是你想象力太丰富
It's your fanciful imaginings.

484
00:35:25,492 --> 00:35:27,660
帮帮我
Help me.

485
00:35:27,662 --> 00:35:29,362
来人啊!
Someone!

486
00:35:29,364 --> 00:35:31,264
帮帮我!
Help me!!

487
00:35:34,135 --> 00:35:37,870
我看见耶稣基督 神的儿子
I saw Jesus Christ, the son of God.

488
00:35:37,872 --> 00:35:42,074
你怎敢奢求救赎 扫罗
How can you hope for salvation, Saul,

489
00:35:42,076 --> 00:35:44,277
明知你的双手沾满了耶稣信徒的
when you have the blood of those who chose Jesus

490
00:35:44,279 --> 00:35:46,045
鲜血?
on your hands?

491
00:35:48,383 --> 00:35:49,949
你说得对
You're right.

492
00:35:52,387 --> 00:35:55,521
你说得对
You're right.

493
00:35:55,523 --> 00:35:56,622
我希望...
And I hope...

494
00:35:58,359 --> 00:36:02,929
那些被我迫害过的人...
that all the people I persecuted...

495
00:36:02,931 --> 00:36:05,598
他们可以发自内心地原谅我
they can find it in their hearts to forgive me.

496
00:36:08,636 --> 00:36:12,205
我已经不是那个你们理应憎恨的人了
I'm not the same man you once had reason to hate.

497
00:36:13,241 --> 00:36:16,375
我以前眼盲
I was blind.

498
00:36:16,377 --> 00:36:18,344
而如今目明了
Now I see.

499
00:36:25,019 --> 00:36:27,787
巴拿巴
Barnabas.

500
00:36:31,092 --> 00:36:35,695
扫罗想受洗接受耶稣
Saul wants to be baptized to accept Jesus.

501
00:36:38,132 --> 00:36:40,233
我们怎能拒绝他呢?
How can we deny him that?

502
00:37:01,322 --> 00:37:04,056
耶稣拣选了你
Jesus has chosen you

503
00:37:04,058 --> 00:37:09,959
要在外邦人和君王并以色列人面前...
to proclaim his name to the world...to the gentiles, their kings, 

504
00:37:09,961 --> 00:37:12,198
宣扬他的名
and the sons of Israel.

505
00:37:13,301 --> 00:37:16,535
我奉圣父 圣子和圣灵的名
I baptize you in the name of the father and of the son 

506
00:37:16,537 --> 00:37:17,703
为你洗礼
and of the Holy Spirit.

507
00:37:28,616 --> 00:37:30,716
我受洗了
I'm baptized.

508
00:37:30,718 --> 00:37:33,619
我受洗了
I'm baptized.

509
00:37:37,859 --> 00:37:42,361
现在我可以传扬耶稣基督的道了!
Now I can spread the word of Jesus Christ!

510
00:37:43,531 --> 00:37:49,702
如果他原谅我 我会在耶稣里面得了丰盛!
If he will forgive me, I will be complete in Jesus!

511
00:37:49,704 --> 00:37:51,404
巴拿巴!
Barnabas!

512
00:37:57,679 --> 00:37:59,745
流便! 你怎么了?
Reuben! What's happened to you?

513
00:37:59,747 --> 00:38:01,247
你在这儿干嘛?
What are you doing here?

514
00:38:01,249 --> 00:38:03,516
- 我... 我不得不走来  - 什么?
- I... I had to walk.  - What?

515
00:38:03,518 --> 00:38:05,585
他... 他说
He... he said everything

516
00:38:05,587 --> 00:38:07,453
我们自以为知道的一切都是错的
that we thought we knew was wrong.

517
00:38:07,455 --> 00:38:08,521
谁? 谁说的?
Who? Who did?

518
00:38:08,523 --> 00:38:09,689
扫罗
Saul.

519
00:38:11,059 --> 00:38:13,125
他已经成了耶稣的信徒了
He's become a follower of Jesus.

520
00:38:15,063 --> 00:38:16,796
这主意很糟
This is a very bad idea.

521
00:38:16,798 --> 00:38:17,863
告诉他
Tell him.

522
00:38:17,865 --> 00:38:19,865
扫罗 你不能在犹太会堂
Saul, you can't preach the word of Jesus

523
00:38:19,867 --> 00:38:21,033
传耶稣的道
inside the synagogue.

524
00:38:21,035 --> 00:38:22,268
我们恰恰必须这样做
That is exactly what we have to do.

525
00:38:22,270 --> 00:38:23,703
我明白你已经习惯
I understand that you're used to

526
00:38:23,705 --> 00:38:25,471
仰仗权威的力量
having the weight of the authorities behind you.

527
00:38:25,473 --> 00:38:27,707
如果他拣选我来宣扬他的名
If I have been chosen to proclaim his name,

528
00:38:27,709 --> 00:38:29,609
那最好是今日而非明日
better I do it today than tomorrow,

529
00:38:29,611 --> 00:38:31,744
最好是此时而非彼刻
better this hour than the next.

530
00:38:34,916 --> 00:38:36,515
最好是此刻
Better this moment.

531
00:38:42,991 --> 00:38:44,991
聚一下! 听我说!
Gather 'round! Listen to me!

532
00:38:44,993 --> 00:38:47,660
我带来了消息!
I bring news!

533
00:38:47,662 --> 00:38:50,763
我认为 只需要小小改变
I think, with a few changes

534
00:38:50,765 --> 00:38:52,798
和一些想象力...
and a little imagination...

535
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:54,500
别操之过急了
Don't get ahead of yourselves.

536
00:38:54,502 --> 00:38:56,602
提庇留还没做决定呢
Tiberius hasn't made his decision yet.

537
00:38:56,604 --> 00:38:59,805
作为我的继任者 我为你做出了一个好榜样
I made a good case for you as my successor.

538
00:38:59,807 --> 00:39:01,173
你永远不知道会发生什么
You never know what could happen.

539
00:39:01,175 --> 00:39:02,508
好了
Enough of this.

540
00:39:02,510 --> 00:39:04,644
我们得到了想要的
We have what we wanted.

541
00:39:04,646 --> 00:39:06,779
知足就好
Let's just be grateful.

542
00:39:10,485 --> 00:39:16,555
我... 以为你随着大帝离开了
I... thought you left with the emperor.

543
00:39:16,557 --> 00:39:19,291
这多好啊?
Isn't that sweet?

544
00:39:19,293 --> 00:39:22,194
一对毒蛇刚要离开
As one pair of vipers prepare to leave,

545
00:39:22,196 --> 00:39:25,031
另一对就打算搬进来了
another plans to move in.

546
00:39:25,033 --> 00:39:28,467
我的朋友! 我就知道他们不能把我们分开
My friend! I knew they couldn't keep us apart.

547
00:39:32,006 --> 00:39:35,041
我带来了消息...
I bring news...

548
00:39:35,043 --> 00:39:37,343
非常不好的消息
very grave news.

549
00:39:40,848 --> 00:39:42,882
提庇留大帝...
Emperor Tiberius...

550
00:39:45,653 --> 00:39:47,586
驾崩了
is dead.

551
00:39:59,100 --> 00:40:02,101
出人意料
It's shocking news.

552
00:40:02,103 --> 00:40:04,670
我真是...
I was...

553
00:40:04,672 --> 00:40:07,073
非常震惊
shocked.

554
00:40:07,075 --> 00:40:09,175
但我们应该感恩
We must be thankful.

555
00:40:09,177 --> 00:40:13,012
我听说他睡在床上... 走得很安详
I'm told he died peacefully... in his bed.

556
00:40:22,123 --> 00:40:28,461
你在期待罗马的新职位吗?
Were you looking forward to your new position in Rome?

557
00:40:47,682 --> 00:40:49,248
多可惜啊
Such a shame.

558
00:40:50,518 --> 00:40:55,020
你的丈夫在这个宫殿里
Your husband, in this palace,

559
00:40:55,022 --> 00:40:58,991
用刀抵着我的喉咙
held a blade against my throat.

560
00:41:01,395 --> 00:41:03,429
他真的很想我死
He really wanted me dead.

561
00:41:05,199 --> 00:41:07,333
过去的就过去吧?
Can't that be left in the past?

562
00:41:09,103 --> 00:41:10,603
没错
Yes.

563
00:41:10,605 --> 00:41:13,239
你说得对
You're right.

564
00:41:13,241 --> 00:41:16,108
让我们关注当下
